divs: sighting detailsabout 9:00 pm my husband called me and our children outside to observe 2 objects facing west and coming from south ascending north. they were bright red\orange and seemed to be blinking. the first one reached a certain height and seemed to just disappear. then the next one disappeared then 3 more came from the same direction. all of them seemed to just disappear. my husband took a photo and it looks like a ball of fire in the photo. there were airplanes that were flying higher than the fireball looking objects. they were clearly different.
